            <title>[HBASE-5845] Single Put should use RetriesExhaustedWithDetailsException in case any exception</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-5845</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-5824&quot; title=&quot;HRegion.incrementColumnValue is not used in trunk&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-5824&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-5824&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, attempt was made to handle single Put execution separately. Put has two exception paths thereafter. It&apos;s better to keep one exception for easy exception handling.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
